mimicking natural processes,

00:53:27.150 --> 00:53:29.780
and so it's things
like figuring out

00:53:29.780 --> 00:53:32.160
less toxic ways
to make black dye,

00:53:32.160 --> 00:53:39.500
or how to create fans that
use less energy basically

00:53:39.500 --> 00:53:42.080
by studying how nature
does these things.

00:53:42.080 --> 00:53:44.940
And they have these
just incredible stories

00:53:44.940 --> 00:53:49.700
of companies who figured out
more efficient, less waste,

00:53:49.700 --> 00:53:52.870
less resources wasted in
the production of products

00:53:52.870 --> 00:53:54.860
and in the way they make things.

00:53:54.860 --> 00:53:57.850
Biomimicry-- it's a
great site and they

00:53:57.850 --> 00:54:01.132
have some really great examples
of things companies are doing.

